util.graph

Class EdgeList<E extends DirectedEdge<?,E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.graph.EdgeList<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the edge type of the graph
    All Implemented Interfaces:

    public final class EdgeList<E extends DirectedEdge<?,E>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Meldable<EdgeList<E>>, java.lang.Iterable<E>
    A linked list of edges for a graph that supports concatenation in O(1).
